30
00:01:41,760 --> 00:01:43,559
Back then, marrying your father

31
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:46,450
was just a means to avenge
the blood feud from ten years ago.

32
00:01:51,360 --> 00:01:54,290
But now, the one
I love is the Third Prince.

33
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:58,330
Wan'er and I love each other.

34
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:02,010
Why must you stand in our way?

35
00:02:06,080 --> 00:02:07,690
Love each other?

36
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:09,330
You were just her first love.

37
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:11,410
First love knows nothing about love.

38
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:12,879
You're the one interfering here.

39
00:02:12,880 --> 00:02:14,799
No, Yan Lidong, what's wrong with you?

40
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:16,039
You're the one who's got issues.

41
00:02:16,040 --> 00:02:18,279
We're filming, you know?
You're the one with issues.

42
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:20,040
- You're the one with issues.
- Your brain is broken.

43
00:02:20,040 --> 00:02:20,639
Say that again.

44
00:02:20,640 --> 00:02:21,839
I just did. So what?

45
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:23,159
Think I won't hit you right now?

46
00:02:23,160 --> 00:02:24,330
Come down here.

47
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:25,879
Come here.

48
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:26,839
Come up here.

49
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:27,890
Come down here.

50
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,570
What are you two doing?

51
00:02:29,600 --> 00:02:31,079
This is a film set!

52
00:02:31,080 --> 00:02:32,079
Not the place to settle

53
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:33,490
your personal grudges.

54
00:02:34,040 --> 00:02:34,999
Calm down, Director.

55
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:38,480
One is Huanxi Entertainment's top star,
the other is Xitu Entertainment's hottest rookie.

56
00:02:38,480 --> 00:02:39,079
Let's go.

57
00:02:39,080 --> 00:02:41,559
Come on, everyone, back to positions.
Get ready for the next take.

58
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:43,519
- We have to do it all over again.
- Enough already.

59
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:44,730
I'm not shooting anymore!

60
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:46,730
Cool down, Lidong.

61
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:52,170
That's a wrap for today.

62
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:54,890
Chenxi.

63
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:04,210
Thank you.

64
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:06,570
I'll practice lines with you again.

65
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:12,119
Lidong,

66
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:13,730
can you help me with something?

67
00:03:21,040 --> 00:03:22,450
Do you think this is right for us?

68
00:03:43,200 --> 00:03:44,930
Mu Chenxi,
are you doing this on purpose?

69
00:03:45,200 --> 00:03:46,410
And if I am?

70
00:03:47,200 --> 00:03:48,250
Does it hurt?

71
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:56,290
Lidong, I'm fine.

72
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:04,999
Chenxi. Let's go watch a movie tonight.

73
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:07,450
Lidong, let's go out for dinner tonight.

74
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:15,919
Sure.

75
00:04:15,920 --> 00:04:17,010
What should we eat?

76
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:21,079
Sure.

77
00:04:21,080 --> 00:04:22,290
What movie are we watching?

78
00:04:22,520 --> 00:04:23,370
Anything's fine.

79
00:04:24,320 --> 00:04:25,290
Let's go.

80
00:04:25,440 --> 00:04:26,290
Yeah.

81
