The movie's about to start.

87
00:05:02,840 --> 00:05:03,810
Chenxi.

88
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:06,770
What did you just say?

89
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:08,519
I said the movie is about to start.

90
00:05:08,520 --> 00:05:10,010
Let's go pick up our tickets.

91
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:14,570
Can we go another day?

92
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:18,330
What's wrong? Are you feeling unwell?

93
00:05:18,960 --> 00:05:21,730
No, I'm just a little tired.

94
00:05:21,840 --> 00:05:22,730
Sorry.

95
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:26,490
It's fine. We'll go another day.

96
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:28,290
Sorry.

97
00:05:37,320 --> 00:05:38,650
I'll head home now.

98
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:40,519
