103
00:05:59,080 --> 00:06:00,890
I'm not eating. Go by yourself.

104
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:16,839
Weren't you watching a movie?

105
00:06:16,840 --> 00:06:17,839
Why are you back?

106
00:06:17,840 --> 00:06:20,130
My phone ran out of battery.
Came back to charge it.

107
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:23,079
Didn't you say
you were going out for dinner?

108
00:06:23,080 --> 00:06:24,610
Why are you eating instant noodles?

109
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:28,530
I wasn't full.
Just eating a little more.

110
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:31,530
Enjoy.

111
00:06:50,880 --> 00:06:51,959
Ms. Lin.

112
00:06:51,960 --> 00:06:55,719
This event is mainly
to introduce Xitu's S+ project.

113
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:56,599
At the same time,

114
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:59,320
it's an opportunity
to promote our rising talents.

115
00:06:59,320 --> 00:07:01,799
All the materials have been compiled
and sent to headquarters.

116
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:02,559
Good.

117
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:04,610
You can handle this as you see fit.

118
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:08,010
Ms. Lin.

119
00:07:08,080 --> 00:07:08,890
Mr. Su.

120
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:10,479
Long time no see.

121
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:12,890
You're looking great.

122
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:15,850
I have you to thank for that.

123
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:18,679
The company's stock has been soaring.

124
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:20,650
How could I not be in a good mood?

125
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,730
We owe a lot of our success

126
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:24,890
to you, Mr. Su.

127
00:07:27,760 --> 00:07:29,210
That's good to hear.

128
00:07:34,160 --> 00:07:35,439
Now, let me introduce

129
00:07:35,440 --> 00:07:36,759
our company's

130
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:39,050
S+ project.

131
00:07:42,840 --> 00:07:45,130
They say Mr. Su spoils his daughter,

132
00:07:45,400 --> 00:07:46,599
but I never expected

133
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:48,890
he'd let her step into

134
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:51,410
this messy industry.

135
00:07:54,080 --> 00:07:57,519
(Su Yuling)
The project will feature our rising star, Yan Lidong.

136
00:07:57,520 --> 00:07:59,199
Yan Lidong is one of our company's

137
00:07:59,200 --> 00:08:00,559
most promising newcomers.

138
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:02,690
We hope everyone
will keep an eye on him.

139
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:11,050
Mr. Yan rarely makes public appearances.

140
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:15,290
I thought Ms. Lin
was keeping him under wraps.

141
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:22,970
Mu Chenxi!

142
00:08:25,880 --> 00:08:27,130
Mu Chenxi!

143
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:28,490
Coming.

144
00:08:28,640 --> 00:08:29,810
Mu Chenxi!

145
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:30,759
Mu Chenxi...

146
00:08:30,760 --> 00:08:31,559
Ms. Lin.

147
00:08:31,560 --> 00:08:32,570
What's this?

148
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:34,730
Is this how you're
taking care of my son?

149
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:35,959
No...

150
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:36,879
This project...

151
00:08:36,880 --> 00:08:39,450
Isn't having one actress
in the family enough?

152
00:08:41,160 --> 00:08:42,330
Ms. Lin.

153
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:45,690
I'd appreciate it
if you could respect my profession.

154
00:08:45,800 --> 00:08:48,439
Besides, you can't even manage your son.

155
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:49,890
How could I possibly manage him?

156
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:50,959
And anyway,

157
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:53,199
