like me do anything about it?

159
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:56,599
Stop making excuses.

160
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:57,890
What did you say back then?

161
00:08:58,760 --> 00:08:59,759
I'm here to see Lidong.

162
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:00,810
He's not here.

163
00:09:01,760 --> 00:09:03,239
Isn't he perfectly fine now?

164
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:06,850
Healthy, lively, eating and drinking well
and even charming delicate little girls.

165
00:09:08,560 --> 00:09:10,719
Had I known you'd be
so indifferent toward Lidong,

166
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:13,250
I never would've
let you into the Yan family.

167
00:09:13,400 --> 00:09:15,679
For the Yan family to take
in a daughter-in-law like you...

168
00:09:15,680 --> 00:09:17,919
We must've been cursed in a past life.

169
00:09:17,920 --> 00:09:20,170
You think I wanted
to marry into your family?

170
00:09:20,520 --> 00:09:22,079
If it weren't for your son

171
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:24,279
sweet-talking me,
chasing me relentlessly,

172
00:09:24,280 --> 00:09:25,730
deceiving me at every turn,

173
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:27,840
would I have been
blind enough to marry him?

174
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:29,959
What? You married Lidong?

175
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:31,770
Yes, we've been married for a long time!

176
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:41,490
Impossible.

177
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,570
No way.

178
00:09:52,560 --> 00:09:53,890
