Don't come here again.

190
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:31,290
Who cares about your measly paycheck?

191
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:34,650
Who told you to go into acting?

192
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:35,559
I...

193
00:10:35,560 --> 00:10:37,970
(The doctor said
forcing memories on him)

194
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:39,450
(could trigger a relapse.)

195
00:10:41,560 --> 00:10:42,770
Do whatever you want.

196
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:44,490
I can't control you anymore.

197
00:10:59,880 --> 00:11:00,999
Sorry.

198
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:03,090
If she ever comes back, just ignore her.

